{
  "stem": "5188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, I-- I felt very warm to some of these Catholic observances, because there-- there was no animosity there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It felt safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The religious aspect felt safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the outside, the brown shirts, the marching, and-- that was ugly, that felt ugly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I had this dichotomy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The school was safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The teachers were kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They certainly wouldn't permit any of the children to mistreat me in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I felt safe going into the church.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And yet there was this-- this movement afoot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After all, my father was put in jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My-- the store was closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The-- the placards on the door, the swastikas, they was-- it was all around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was there, you know, on the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But still, with all that was going on, there were still Jews-- many of them, even in our own family-- that felt that you shouldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, how can you leave?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can you leave the place where you make a living, and you're comfortable, and-- and everything is-- and you're established, and go off to some other country where you don't know the language, where you don't know what to do?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember sitting in the kitchen of my Aunt Else-- that's my father's older sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vasen-- V-A-S-E-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived in Rodenkirchen, which was the closest to where we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had gone there for the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my Aunt Else, arguing with my father, because my father had said, I am leaving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm taking my family out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not-- there is no future here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, how can you be so irresponsible?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are leaving a place where you have a livelihood, where you can take care of your family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're going off into nowhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
